name: Flavors Restaurant Lombok
about: Fine Casual Dining by The Lombok Lodge Hospitality . FLAVORS Restaurant, nestled within the charming confines of 'The Lombok Lodge, Boutique Hotel, Medana Bay, presents a delightful and unique Fine Casual Dining Experience. . With Chef Jiwa Raga's exceptional Cuisine and the restaurant's unique Wine List, your visit to FLAVORS is an absolute must during your stay in Lombok! . FLAVORS Restaurant is ideally located on the northwestern coast of Lombok, a mere 35-minute drive from Senggigi area. Just 15 minutes away from the enchanting Gili Islands and a short 5 minutes walk from the 'The Oberoi' Hotel. Enjoy the captivating scene as local fishermen ply their craf, casting their nets into the shimmering ocean under the moonlit night sky, in pursuit of the ocean's bounty. . Do not miss the private over-water dining and Chef Jiwa's Signature Lobster Menu! Secure your reservation now online for an unforgettable evening!

about: Kemangi is located right in the heart of Kuta Lombok, 100 M from Kuta beach, which is about 20 minutes driving time from the Lombok International Airport. The design is best described as "modern tropical" with eclectic touches emphasing the local Sasak culture. Kemangi Lombok provide a suave atmosphere for you to enjoy when you're away from home. Combining Western and Asian Fusion, Kemangi Bar & Kitchen offers a complete range of dishes for every taste. We use only the finest, localy-grown and imported ingredients to provide our customer a great breakfast, lunch and diner experience in Lombok. We also have an expansive beverage menu including fresh juice, beer, cocktails, spirits and wine. Restaurant hours are 8 am – 11 pm.

about: Nami by Hani blends Indonesian flavors with global influences, offering a warm and intimate dining experience at Hani Hideaway. Our menu highlights fresh, locally sourced ingredients and personalized service in a relaxed, cozy setting. ✨ À la carte dining – Enjoy lunch (12–6 pm) or dinner (6–10 pm) on the rooftop terrace or in the garden. Walk-ins welcome or book ahead. Family Dinners – A 4-course shared-table experience at 7:30 pm on select evenings. Reservation required. Candlelight Dinners – A romantic 3-course private dinner in the garden, perfect for special occasions. Reservation required. Sunset Picnics – A private beachside setup at 5 pm to enjoy the island’s best sunsets. Pre-booking required. We can’t wait to welcome you to Nami by Hani, where every meal is designed to be memorable.

name: Fat Cats Bar & Restaurant
about: Whether you prefer to sit on the beach with your feet in the sand, or in our cool and breezy elevated bistro, Fat Cats bar and restaurant has it all. Catering for over 100 diners, we serve a wide variety of breakfast, lunch and dinner options including our famous Mexican classics, we now offer a wider variety of options for everyone from the hungry diver to the health conscious vegan. Fat Cats is open daily from 7am until 11pm. Our room guests are invited to enjoy the breakfast buffet from 7am until 10am (outside diners are also welcome). Our a la cart breakfast options are available between 7am and 11.30am and include our famous breakfast burrito, smashed avocado and poached eggs, smoked salmon over rye bread, creamy coconut porridge, smoothie bowls and much more. Lunch includes a range of salads, poke bowls, pasta, burgers, sandwiches or Indonesian and Asian favorites. name: Pinksunset Kiss Gili T
about: Welcome to PinkSunset Kiss at Gili Trawangan! Located on the island’s most iconic sunset spot, PinkSunset Kiss offers breathtaking views of the Lombok Strait and the majestic Bali volcano all at once. Join us every day for live DJ sessions, mesmerizing fire dance shows, soulful saxophone performances — and soon, thrilling live drum sets — as the sun dips below the horizon. Pizza lovers, get ready to indulge: our talented Italian chef, Riccardo from Rome, crafts some of the most delicious, authentic pizzas you’ll ever taste. Come relax, dance, and connect with friends — old and new — in the vibrant and welcoming atmosphere of PinkSunset Kiss. Every visit promises unforgettable moments set against the spectacular natural beauty of Gili Trawangan. See you soon at PinkSunset Kiss – where every sunset is a celebration!

name: MAHAMAYA Gili Meno Restaurant
about: Our stylish restaurant and bar offer stunning views of the beach. Should you tire of gazing across idyllic tropical seas, you can always watch our executive chef Hamzar create mouth-wateringly irresistible dishes in his open kitchen from your table. We cook fresh, simple and – wherever possible – organic food. Our highly acclaimed restaurant delivers delicious food of an International standard – with a twist – carefully created by our executive chef. Enjoy a luxurious lunch or a sublimely romantic evening dinner in one of our popular and magically-lit waterfront beach tables. Cool off from the tropical heat with a refreshing drink at our seafront bar. Or enjoy the perfect end to a perfect day with a classic cocktail and spectacular sunset views.

name: Pachamama Organic Cafe
about: Pachamama Organic Cafe & Private Villa on the north east side of Gili Air, one street behind the main beach road. Take the little alley way in between Kaluku and Orong Villages, and then your first right - you will find us about 100m down on the left. Our menu is focused on fresh, healthy and healing foods - all super delicious and predominantly plant based. You will find a good selection of vegan, vegetarian as well as meat options, lots of yummy juices & smoothies and of course some delicious sweet treats including raw deserts. We also brew our own kombucha. We have designed our dining space to make you feel at home, in a sunny & relaxed courtyard. Our gift shop features a range of beautiful Indonesian textiles, gypsy-inspired clothing, jewellery, accessories, natural products & homewares. We hope to see your face at Pachamama soon!

name: Kenza
about: When you arrive at Kenza you find our tropical terrace, the perfect spot for a social gathering at any time of the day. When you enter Kenza the bartenders will welcome you while preparing your drinks. The modern space cooled by AC’s is great for a quite breakfast, festive lunch, cocktail date or to try our wide variety of wines and dishes. During the day please just walk in, during the night we advice you to book a table. DAYTIME We open early at 7:00 AM for your morning coffee, fresh juices and our all day breakfast and lunch menu. Healthy acai bowls, big breakfasts, green breaky bowls, focaccia sandwiches, main plates and sweets. DINNER TIME Around 5:00 PM Kenza welcomes you for the modern french bistro inspired menu, with excellent bites, sharing plates, high quality meat, seafood and sides, combined with a diverse wine collection. Our professional team is ready to create a social and fun night with our consciously created cocktail menu.

name: My House
about: This unconventional "Locanda" is born one year ago in full pandemic time, As a Chef like many other colleagues I was without a job isolated in Gili Trawangan. I decided so to start cook some food for sell it online. Helped with my sweet wife Tania we were cooking and delivering on all Gili Trawangan. The name My House is because we actually live here and after seeing the good respond of our customers on delivery we decided also to use the backyard of my house for make a small place to eat. We love to keep this atmosphere of traditional "Locanda" The menu is on WhatsApp catalog and change based on available ingredients. We buy ours ingredients from lokal farms, fisherman and butcher for help also the local economy.

name: Ashtari - Slow Food / Yoga / Loft
about: Spoiled with epic views over South Lombok coastline, Ashtari is a must see majestic Spanish styled “Masia”. After Joining the Slow Food revolution, its restaurant & lounge now features a menu rich in local ingredients, exploring a Fusion Kitchen from different Asian cuisines, from Indonesia to India, and also some Western Influences. When the sun hits the horizon it evolves into a bustling scene with delicious curries & wine, craft beers and more unique sharing dishes. From sunrise to sunset, you can practice yoga surrounded by nature, follow cooking classes and appreciate the rich organic items of the vegetable garden. You can even stay overnight and experience the Loft, a 100sqm comfortable seafront apartment with a 18sqm private terrace. Ashtari, Lombok famous icon since 2006.

name: TERRA - Plant Based Food
about: Terra restaurant serves innovative, inspiring and 100% plant based food in the heart of Kuta Lombok. All food is vegan & gluten free. A place indeed where you can nourish your body, mind and soul, and learn through a new culinary experience. Our kitchen is run by passionate Japanese Chef Mamiko Eda, an Ashtanga Yoga lover, with over 10 years experience in vegan and cooked food. The venue will be divided into three different atmospheres. On the first floor, with the street entrance, we will find the takeaway section or healing station; where it will be served breakfast, juices and healthy drinks, as well as a buffet of salads and cakes. The restaurant will be located on the top floor with an indoor and outdoor area. On the same level, we will find the AC lounge area for reading and work, with sofas and bookshelves full of books about nutrition, health, yoga and other subjects. The lounge will be a comfortable sitting area and the cosy corner of the venue.

name: Markisa Restaurant
about: Sun is an ingredient at Markisa, the Indonesian word for passion fruit. We thought it only fitting to name our restaurant after the fruit that takes centre stage in the design of the restaurant and hotel. Markisa finds its roots in honest Mediterranean cooking, with a bit of an Italian bias. We will be working closely with local organic farmers and fishermen and believe strongly in respecting the integrity of our ingredients. We strive to produce as much yummy goodness in house, in a way nona would be proud of. From slow ferment naturally leavened breads to preserving peppers, hand rolling pasta and curing sardines. We Love food, like really love it, and hope that you can taste it in our cooking.

name: Klub Kembali
about: South Lombok’s craft cocktail destination, focusing on spirits, wine and beer produced in Indonesia. Unique cocktails with a twist of Lombok. Indonesian and fusion cuisine to enjoy with your drinks, coffees, and Sunday games on our own Bocce Ground. All in an over 100 year old Joglo filled with art, upcycled interiors, and vintage music from our record player. In addition to providing the best cocktail experience, we are aiming to run our bar as a closed loop system to reduce waste. Most of our suppliers take their bottles back to be reused or recycled, all our beers come in cans, which are easily recycled. And plastic is recycled by a local bank sampah or our sister company, Plastik Kembali.

name: Omah Cobek Restaurant
about: Starting from our love of the traditional cuisine of Java (especially Yogyakarta) hard we encountered on the island of Lombok that time, and we see the lack of diversity of culinary in Mataram (2008), then with a capital of family recipes, we want to share the experience of taste to be enjoyed by foodies on the island of Lombok. Also based on the survey, the food is very spicy flavor arouse your appetite Indonesian society, especially the island of Lombok. True to its name "York" which means "chili" in Javanese, the island of Lombok has chili is more spicy than other regions in Indonesia, we are determined to present a traditional Indonesian dishes are made from chili (chili) as for the name we chose was omah mortar. Omah in the Java language means house, while cobek is a tool to smooth spice and often used to make the sauce, so it is "Omah cobek" is the home of a mortar which means lots of available-chili sauce. Based on the name, Omah cobek is a restaurant with the peculiarities of various kinds of sauce appetizing. Finally, with determination and courage and invoke the aid of the Lord Almighty we opened our first outlet in Jl.Maktal 6 Mataram on January 11, 2009.

name: Datu Restaurant & Bar
about: Nestled on the serene shores of Gili Trawangan, our restaurant is a celebration of flavors from across Asia and beyond. Designed as a semi fine-dining destination, we offer a curated menu that blends the boldness of Indian spices, the artistry of Asian fusion, the warmth of traditional Indonesian dishes, and the timeless appeal of Western favorites. Dine under the stars or beside the sea, surrounded by gentle ocean breezes and island charm. Each plate is thoughtfully crafted to reflect depth, balance, and creativity-bringing together the best of culinary traditions in a setting that soothes the senses. Perfect for romantic evenings, special celebrations, or relaxed dinners with a touch of elegance.

name: Molly's Bar and Grill
about: Molly's is roughly 5 minutes north of Senggigi,situated directly across the road from Quinci Villas,a popular resort in the village of Mangsit. There are several resorts within walking distance of Molly's Bar and Grill including Puri Mas,The Alang Alang,Holiday Resort Lombok and several others. Molly's is a family operated business specializing in BBQ ,Seafood and Indonesian dishes. Molly's has large screen TV's for sports viewing and hosts a friendly bar for cold drinks, snacks and music. A dart board also adds flavor to this warm and welcoming venue. For sports enthusiasts from around the globe Molly's staff will always endeavor to find your game. For deep sea fishing,snorkeling and ocean exploring, Molly's Bar and Grill hosts the Lombok Fish and Game from Medana Bay Marina and activities can be organized directly at the Restaurant.

name: Bella Ciao Pizzeria & Italian Restaurant
about: Bella ciao restaurant and pizzeria offers "Pizza alla Romana" is typically a place that offers a wide range of Roman-style pizzas, known for its thin and crispy dough. The main room is furnished to reflect a convivial and welcoming atmosphere. The tables and chairs are often made of wood that evoke a rustic and traditional style. The arrangement of the tables is designed to optimize the space and ensure comfort for customers. And at the same time you can enjoy a wonderful and colorful sunset central area is dedicated to the preparation of pizzas. Here you will find the oven, which can be wood-fired, and all the equipment needed to prepare the dough and toppings. The preparation area is often visible to customers, offering a view of the making of the pizzas. The establishment is designed to offer an authentic and comfortable dining experience, reflecting the essence of Roman cuisine and the love for quality pizza.

We offer a wide range of cuisines and drinks to choose from. The ambiance, taste, and hospitality would make you comfortable and we strive to make your holiday the most memorable one for your lifetime. We are located at North Lombok regency area to welcome you for a serene dining experience. At Camilla beach club you can experience fresh food, serene music, clean environment, refreshing drinks and proximity to the Bintang beach. name: Lumbung Restaurant
about:
The award winning Lumbung Restaurant at The Oberoi, Lombok takes its name from the traditional rice storage containers that are integral to daily life on Lombok.
Located within the lush hotel gardens, Lumbung Restaurant includes an open sided, thatched structure and an al fresco courtyard. Once a week, guests are entertained by traditional Balinese dancers and musicians performing in the adjacent amphitheatre.
The menu features Indonesian, Western and Indian cuisine, topped off with delicious imported cheese, homemade ice creams and sorbets. We also offer a range of sugar free desserts and a special Children's menu. 
Lumbung Restaurant also hosts special dining nights. Please contact +62 370 6138 444 for reservation.

name: Le Bistro
about:
Closed until March 2019 for Renovation

Le Bistro is a french fusion food restaurant located on the beach, facing the mount Rinjani. Owned by french friends, the head chef is also French. We get our inspiration from various countries and accomodate them with the local style. We are specialized in fresh raw tuna. The Tuna Tartare, Tuna Ceviche and Tuna Tataki are our signature dishes. We also propose grilled fish fillet, meats, burgers, and a wide range of imported wine. We use only fresh ingredients and we rinse the vegetables with drinkable water, so you can go for salads as well. All the breads we use for our sandwiches and burgers are home-made We have great barmen to do good cocktails and last but not least, awesome chocolate brownies and gelato to finish your meal. All the team will do his best to host you and provide you the best possible service, but please, don't forget that you are on holidays, on a small remote island with a different culture and education, and a different relation to the time. Enjoy that ;)

name: Cafe Rinjani Dawn
about: Cafe Rinjani Dawn is a cozy, informal restaurant located at the start of the Senaru Waterfall Trail. Known for its authentic Indonesian cuisine and locally sourced coffee, the cafe offers stunning views of rice terraces stretching down to a distant ocean. Whether you’re enjoying traditional dishes, a freshly made pizza, or just relaxing with a cup of coffee, Cafe Rinjani Dawn provides a welcoming atmosphere for all. Popular in the evenings, it's the perfect spot to unwind with an ice-cold beer or a cool glass of wine after a day of exploring Lombok. As part of the Rinjani Dawn Adventures family, we’re committed to supporting the local community through our Sasak Warriors initiative. By dining with us, you’re contributing to efforts that provide food aid, support education, and promote sustainability in Senaru. Whether you're fueling up before a trek or enjoying a laid-back evening, Cafe Rinjani Dawn is the perfect spot to enhance your Lombok adventure.

name: Curfew Restaurant And Beer Garden
about: Looking for some great craft beer, exceptional food, or just a place to kick back and relax? We've got you covered. We're proud to offer a fantastic selection of local craft beers that are all brewed right here in Indonesia. From hoppy IPA's to smooth lagers, we've got something on tap for everyone. If cocktails are more your thing, don't sweat it, we've got plenty to choose from. Our menu features a huge variety of locally sourced goods, from the highest quality produce to fresh fish caught daily. We work hard with our team of chefs and farmers to ensure that every dish we serve is thoughtfully prepared with the best ingredients available. Our commitment to sustainably and locally sourced food has given us the opportunity to explore the best that Lombok has to offer and support our local community. Right in the heart of Kuta, Lombok, Curfew is the perfect place to unwind and enjoy excellent food and drinks.

name: Serene Sunset
about: SERENE SUNSET BEACH is located on the beautiful sunset-side of the island, perfect for relaxing beach days and beautiful sunsets! Our big passion is to take care of our Environment, Mother Nature. This is way we banned Plastic and Cans totally from our Menu! We offer you always fresh ingredients and always made with lots of love! On the Menu you find our famous, refreshing Mojito's, fresh Organic Juices, tropical Fruits and of course not to forget our homemade Pizza and Pasta! SERENE SUNSET is our home which we work hard with our hearts to make it as enjoyable and comfortable as possible - and we love to share our little piece of heaven with you! Feel Home and safe with us, if you have any special request or concern, there will always be someone to help you! Again, we are on a little tiny Island in the middle of nowhere with limited access to actually everything, so lets just chill, relax and appreciate life more together:) We're looking forward to have you in Serene Sunset!

name: Sunrise Beach Club
about: Fusion Style Reflecting our guests from all over the world, the Sunrise Beach Club menu offers Fusion style modern dishes, Tapas and Indonesian Specialities all day long; with a hard to beat BBQ at nighttime. A dedicated kids menu makes sure our little guests are also taken care of. Selected Wine For those who love their wines, we offer selected good quality French and Italian wines at reasonable prices, something hard to find on Gili Air. For Champagne lovers we offer Jean Pierre Brut, Lanson and Bollinger. 75m Beach Front With 75 meters direct beach front Sunrise Beach Club has 2 main beach seating areas. The wooden sundeck invites for both lounging and eating directly above the sand with direct sea views and open skies. Diversity The Beach Club offers various seating areas for different tastes with one menu throughout. You can also watch the gentle turquoise waves from our covered beach restaurant area, which is decked out with white washed rattan furniture.

about: Bahia is a beachfront restaurant and bar on Gili Air, offering island-fusion cuisine, tropical cocktails and a relaxed atmosphere right on the sand. Guests can choose from sunbeds, lounge chairs, shaded tables, comfy couches or indoor seating. Our menu highlights fresh, colorful dishes made with quality ingredients ideal for sharing or enjoying on your own. Whether you stop by for a swim or snorkel just in front, come for a long lazy lunch, or unwind with cocktails at sunset, Bahia brings together friendly service, comfort, and a beautiful oceanfront setting that makes every visit memorable.

name: Flowers & Fire Wholefoods Cafe
about: Situated under a sprawling sapodilla tree and our Flowers & Fire Yoga Garden, our open air plant based cafe serves simple but delicious whole food creations with plenty of fresh, minimally processed and enzyme rich ingredients. Everything, from our bread, to our peanut butter, to our dressings and sauces are made from scratch using healthy and whole ingredients. We cater to vegetarian and vegan diets, offering meals that are satisfying, artfully crafted and will leave you feeling balanced. Our food philosophy is that simple, hearty, fresh, healthy, digestible and delicious food is best. But there is always space for good coffee and an extensive tea selection. And wait until you try our homemade “I can’t believe it’s not Ben & Jerry’s” raw vegan, creamy fresh fruit ice cream, served with a crackly cacoa topping and sliced sapodilla from our tree. Not only will our inviting cafe nourish you, but we also offer poolside community wifi facilities for digital nomads visiting Gili Air.

name: Zorba The Greek
about: Zorba the Greek / Go Veggies Go Vegan is the only one restaurant plant based joint and mediteranian cuisine in Lombok. We used to think that plant-based diet is impossible, compelled by our love and respect for mother earth as well as a desire for a healthier lifestyle we decided to do something radical, we have never look back. We’re committed to making most amazing burgers and vegan food in Lombok. We break the stereotype of burgers, sandwiches, vegan food. In short, we rock with plant-based burgers, sandwiches, soups and delicious vegan food and more. Zorba the Greek / Go Veggies Go Vegan is semi outdoor building, next to vegetables garden of Anggrek Putih Eco Resort. Most of our ingredients freshly cut from our own garden. Visiting our restaurant, you can take free tour to our organic vegetable garden, so from the farm to your plate. Non vegetarian menu is available.

name: Restaurant Codium
about: Codium is a beachside restaurant in Lombok, located near the shores of Kuta. We serve Mediterranean-inspired dishes alongside fresh Indonesian flavors, with a special focus on local seaweed, seafood, and seasonal vegetables. Whether you’re looking for a relaxed restaurant by the beach in Lombok or a unique dining experience with ocean views, we are the place to be! Our open-fire kitchen showcases the island’s finest ingredients — with a special focus on amazing locally line-caught seafood — prepared simply and beautifully in a style inspired by the Mediterranean. Relax with your feet in the sand, enjoying Sunset, while our chefs cook over the flames, pairing each dish with a thoughtful selection of wines and crafted cocktails. Soft light, ocean breeze, and soulful flavors create a warm, intimate atmosphere that makes every dinner at Codium memorable.

name: SANDS Beach Club Gili Air
about: SANDS Beach Club & Restaurant is an all-day hangout and beachfront dining spot on Gili Air, designed to follow the relaxed rhythm of island life. Start your day with freshly baked pastries, sourdough bread, and quality coffee from our in-house bakery. Spend the afternoon by the pool or on the beach enjoying light lunches, fresh dishes, and refreshing drinks. As the sun sets, SANDS transforms into a relaxed yet vibrant dinner spot with handcrafted cocktails and a menu featuring fresh seafood, high quality steak, pizza, sushi and island-inspired mains. Welcoming families, couples, solo travellers, and locals alike, SANDS offers a laid-back atmosphere without any pressure... just good food, great drinks, and beautiful ocean views from morning to night. Whether you’re stopping by for breakfast, spending the day by the pool, or joining us for sunset cocktails and dinner, SANDS is the perfect place to experience all-day living on Gili Air.

name: Bar Captikus
about: Captikus is a hidden speak easy bar located behind an old Chinese-Indonesian pharmacy. "Toko Obat" in Indonesia. The bar transports you back in time and takes great pride in their Indonesian inspired cocktail menu. Indonesia is also called “The Mother of Spices” and these distinctive spices can be found back in multiple cocktails throughout the menu. Captikus does not only focusses on Indonesian flavours but also dedicate a big part of their menu for “Classics” and “Modern Classics”. A Hidden Gem in Kuta Lombok Step into Captikus, where the vibrant spirit of Indonesia meets the elegance of a speakeasy. Tucked away in Kuta Lombok, our bar offers an enchanting escape, blending the rich flavors of local ingredients with the timeless allure of classic cocktails.

name: Amatera Restaurant
about: Experience a range of delicious flavors and dining experiences at Kalandara Restaurant. A selection of authentic local cuisine and international cuisine such are also available to enjoy. An extended outdoor area offers a sweeping view over the entire property and the blue of the ocean and sound of the waves offered by nature, participate to accompany you. It is open for breakfast every morning, offering a delicious choice of different options. From international favorites and healthy fare to local style dishes and signature specialties, our culinary team understands the importance of a good breakfast to start the day off right. For the dinner, Kalandara Restaurant transforms into a romantic environment complete with elegant table settings and mood music drifting through the night air. A semi-fine dining menu takes guests on a flavorful journey of culinary excellence driven by sustainably sourced ingredients from the land and sea

name: Selong Selo Resort & Residences
about: Discover Selong Selo Resort & Residences, a luxury villa resort in South Lombok, Indonesia. Our award-winning resort offers breathtaking ocean views, private infinity pools, and bespoke villas that blend modern comfort with natural elegance. Enjoy world-class amenities, including gourmet dining at Aura Lounge and Bar, a wellness spa, and access to a range of outdoor activities from surfing to local cultural tours. Committed to sustainability and cultural preservation, Selong Selo provides an unforgettable escape that harmonizes luxury and nature. Experience the tranquility and charm of Lombok with us.
